{"type":"message","id":"32319903","parentId":"74a0d6fe","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:40:10.657Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've completed the autonomous learning task and saved the key findings to the learning notes file.","thinkingSignature":"52cf8cb176adfa5f4e9b644ca2a4233ab09443f255ff886da6a5d6044b01a029"},{"type":"text","text":"已完成自主学习并保存。梳理了以下3个行业的关键动态：\n\n**企业数字化转型**：制造业数字化改造率已达89.6%，国产化成强制标准，全栈替代（芯片/OS/数据库）成政企项目准入门槛。\n\n**智能安防**：AI大模型重构行业，端侧AI误报率降至0.8%，民用市场进入黄金三年，芯片涨价周期开启（核心CIS涨价10-20%）。\n\n**IT运维服务**：AIOps 3.0时代来临，大模型推动运维自治化，人工干预降至10%以内，运维从成本中心升级为战略支点。\n\n内容已保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4979,"output":171,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49131,"cost":{"input":0.0014937,"output":0.0002052,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0030183299999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775065205691}}
